
top    -- show live system activity
It shows what is happening inside your system right now
You can see:
CPU usage
RAM usage
Running processes
Process IDs (PID)
Which app is using how much resource

htop   -- better version of top
df -h  -- check disk-space
du -sh -- folder size
free -m -- memory(ram)
uptime -- system running time
iostat  -- disk performance
ss -tulnp -- check network issue
